<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ح و ض<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٥٠٦ - ح و ض]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حوَّضَ يحوِّض، تحويضًا، فهو مُحوِّض، والمفعول مُحوَّض <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• حوَّض فلانٌ:</span> عَمِل حَوْضًا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• حوَّض حولَ الشَّيء:</span> دارَ حوله <span class="c1">"حوَّض حولَ الموضوع لضبط عناصره"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• حوَّض الماءَ:</span> جمعَه في حَوْضٍ ونحوه.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>